To investigate the effect of B-RAF and MEK inhibition in melanoma cultures , we used RAF265 ( a pan @-@ RAF inhibitor ) , MEK162 ( a MEK1 @/@ MEK2 inhibitor ) and the MEK inhibitor trametinib .
