WT ( YUVON and YUROB ) , B-RAF mutant ( YUKSI and YUMAC ) and N-RAS mutant ( YUDOSO and YUKIM ) cells were treated with increasing doses ( 10 @-@ 1000 nM ) of MEK162 or left untreated for 4 and 24 hours .
