The 2.2 @-@ kb murine <i> Snail </i> promoter was generated by PCR using a forward primer with an XbaI linker sequence , 5′ @-@ TCTAGAATTGTTTGCTGCTGTATGGTCTTC @-@ 3′ , along with a reverse primer with a BglII linker sequence , 5′ @-@ AGATCTGTTGGCCAGAGCGACCTAG @-@ GTAG @-@ 3′ , and mouse genomic DNA as a template .
