The PCR product was gel purified and ligated into pCRII @-@ TOPO TA vector .
The pre @-@ LIM domain of Ajuba was generated essentially as described [ @<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="pbio-0030011-b09"> 9 </xref>@ ] , but was fused to GFP by subcloning from the pEGFP @-@ N1 20 vector ( BD Biosciences Clontech )
In situ hybridization
The pCRII @-@ TOPO TA vector containing a region of the 3′ UTR of <i> Snail </i> was used as a template to generate digoxigenin @-@ labeled sense and antisense riboprobes ( Roche ) .
The respective probes were obtained by XhoI and BamH1 digestions .
